{"about_the_game":"Unearthing Mars is a VR adventure game set on the mysterious Red Planet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs Co-Pilot of the retrieval team, the player will have the full experience of a space explorer on Mars.<br />\r\nUnearthing Mars provides hours of unique gameplay experiences, ranging from navigating a landing craft through a sandstorm to driving a Mars rover. <br />\r\nFrom puzzle-solving to first-person shooting, the game will allow players to resolve challenges from a variety of game genres.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGameplay:<br />\r\nStory -- Unravel the mysteries of Phobos<br />\r\nSimulation -- Experience space flight and landing through the cockpit<br />\r\nDriving Simulation -- Explore the Red Planet with the rover vehicle<br />\r\nPuzzle -- Solve the remnant puzzles of Phobos<br />\r\nFPS -- Battle against cryptic alien beings<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis product is a VR experience lasting around 2 hours, and is also the first VR product made with Unreal Engine 4 by Winking Entertainment. A number of stages feature various genre of game mechanics and gameplay. Compared to Unearthing Mars on Playstation VR, visual quality has been improved and storyline has been adjusted on PC version.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Chapter 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/605310/935d20d74429e913219d6b9e4df23a2250401c7d.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/605310/ea3e1fbd848b886ebd5fc03ca5462090a742ddc1.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/605310/ca631ec52d8beebaf6996c4cf4b953ed50cee081.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/605310/091d3817ff82982b75cdc0ae204ec1c61e42dde4.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/605310/fb851b9cd6c7ed826e5106014eb3ca0e2fb83fb9.jpg"},{